OL,3,CNew #15 million facility under
OL,4,Cconstruction at Cumberland Infirmary
OL,6,FA new #15 million facility is being
OL,7,Fbuilt at the Cumberland Infirmary in
OL,8,FCarlisle.
OL,10,FConstruction work is underway on the
OL,11,Fnew endoscopy unit at the infirmary
OL,12,Fwhich is set to be able to treat more
OL,13,Fpatients in the county.
OL,15,FThe Cumberland Infirmary facility is
OL,16,Fset to see 99% of patients receive
OL,17,Ftheir diagnostic procedure in six
OL,18,Fweeks and a further capacity for an
OL,19,Fextra 30 lists per week.
