OL,3,CNew #15 million facility under
OL,4,Cconstruction at Cumberland Infirmary
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Dayat Karat,
OL,7,FClinical Director, North Cumbria NHS
OL,8,FTrust said: "Our current facilities
OL,9,Fdate back almost 25 years and we have
OL,10,Fthree rooms at the moment in
OL,11,Fendoscopy, only one of which will be
OL,12,Fsufficient size to meet national
OL,13,Fcriteria.
