OL,3,CNew #15 million facility under
OL,4,Cconstruction at Cumberland Infirmary
OL,6,F"The problem is that the demand for
OL,7,Fendoscopy has increased year on year
OL,8,Fover the last 25 years, and we are now
OL,9,Fin a position where we really can't
OL,10,Fmeet that demand in terms of the
OL,11,Fpatients we need to see but also in
OL,12,Fterms of the quality of the service
OL,13,Fthat's expected in this day and age.
OL,15,F"We have struggled now for a long time
OL,16,Fto provide the service we aspire to
OL,17,Fprovide and having this facility will
OL,18,Fmean that we will have all the tools
OL,19,Fwe need to provide a first class
OL,20,Fservice for people the population of
OL,21,Fnorth Cumbria."
