OL,3,CNew #15 million facility under
OL,4,Cconstruction at Cumberland Infirmary
OL,6,FExcavation of the original site is now
OL,7,Fcomplete and retaining wall structures
OL,8,Fare now starting to go up.
OL,10,FShellie O'Connor, Chief Operating
OL,11,FOfficer said: "It's a faster way of
OL,12,Fbuilding it, it takes off quite a lot
OL,13,Fof time and disruption to the hospital
OL,14,Fsites.
OL,16,F"A traditional construction would take
OL,17,Fa hell of a lot longer. You'd have all
OL,18,Fthe equipment in, all the deliveries
OL,19,Fin.
